title: The Seed-Planting Old Man's Lovey-dovey Sexual Training of a Shut-in
description: A girl hit with the lust of an old man instead awakens her own sexual desire and easily goes along with having sex sure is nice~ That was the kind of book we thought of… But?! An extremely indulging girl who has such a strong sexual appetite that she is in no way inferior to a seed-planting uncle is also nice…
author: Kirin Kakeru
